GENERAL HOTEL SERVICES

Customer services

Customer service;
Swimming pool and spa centre offering sauna, hydromassage, solarium, and steam bath services;
Gym with modern fitness equipment;
Massage facilities;
Roof Garden with views of the Thermaikos Bay, the harbour of
Platamonas and Mount Olympus;
3 lifts;
Direct-dial telephone;
Individual heating and air conditioning;
Underground parking;
Room service;
Laundry service;
Business services - venues;
Small meeting room;
CCTV;
24-hr security
The hotel offers 17 standard rooms and 2 suites.
All rooms have individual heating and air conditioning, cable TV, DVD player, phone, safety box, electric locks, free internet access, mini bar, hairdryer. Suites also have a hydromassage tub, laptop and fax.
